author: Anjana George
title: Honey Rose, Mohanlal song for Kanal released
text:
Pathukke Entho..., a romantic song from M Padmakumar's upcoming movie, Kanal, starring Honey Rose and Mohanlal was released on October 16.
The song is composed by Ouseppachan and sung by Neha Nair.
The cinema , Kanal, with the tagline, every end has an old beginning, is scripted by S Suresh Babu. Apart from Mohanlal and Honey, the film has Anoop Menon, Atul Kulkarni, Honey Rose, Nikita Thukral and Sheelu Abraham.
